0.2.4
-----
    - graph_utils() added.

0.2.3
-----
    - "config()"" now returns the parameters and the logger in two separated
    values, instead of returning logger inside the parameters.
    - The default parameters filename is ".pyground.yaml" and it is first
    searched in the current working directory. If not found, then it is searched
    in the home folder.

0.2.2
-----
    - Changed the method that computes the toy dataset.
